      <br>
      • Language-based regional cooperation with innovation practice organisations
      <br>
      • Production of «visual discussion materials» on innovative practice examples (short films)
      <br>
      • Production of theoretically informed case studies from film material
      <br>    
      • Feedback from stakeholder groups EU-wide
      <br>
      • Cross national workshops on Innovative Service Delivery
      <br>    
      • Preparation of a research agenda
